  - ONE appended components CSV (all ears): <out_dir>/ear_components_appended.csv
        columns: ear_id, component_index, size_voxels, branching_deg>=3,
                 endpoints_deg==1, isolated_deg==0, is_lcc

No per-ear component CSVs and no .xyz files are written.

Requires:
  pip install numpy trimesh scikit-image open3d
